  "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/tarball/2.2.3",
  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/zipball/2.2.3",
  "body": "## Updates:\r\n- Synced translations from the [Weblate project](https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/zalithlauncher2/)\r\n- Control layout: added support for copying control layouts to a new file\r\n\r\n## Changes:\r\n- Joystick: the movable range is now determined by the background shape\r\n\r\n## Fixes:\r\n- NeoForge: fixed failure to properly detect and download versions 26.1+\r\n- Update loader: fixed incorrect logic when waiting for the loader list\r\n- Resolution: now calculated using only the Surface size\r\n- LWJGL: fixed missing legacy stb API causing some mods to fail to run properly. by [ShirosakiMio](https://github.com/ShirosakiMio)",
